係咪好嬲呀？</span></span></strong>」。//<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\nDLLM 死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"6e41e79deb310913f68936330b734f9cad328428","tid":1465230,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T14:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZXNagjg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZXNagjg.jpg&h=9b5bd145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a92d4973fdf689fbc3cdb620cc5d2dfc1c1806b8","tid":1465230,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T17:39:53.000Z","msg":"皇軍死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3852fa9f0d9960841da1a7e8810722fa12086f28","tid":1465230,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T16:22:26.000Z","msg":"死差佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea8060d789d9fbfe8f16a000d5220854fed23b5","tid":1465230,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:42:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/eAOMSBH.png\" />"}]}